#: ../../source/nvl_mode.rst:228
msgid ""
"If not None, this is the click-to-continue indicator that is used for NVL "
"mode characters that are at the end of a page. (That is, immediately "
"followed by an nvl clear statement.) This replaces the ctc parameter of :"
"func:`Character`."
